149
00:12:17.340 --> 00:12:18.740
Nu. absolut nimic.

150
00:12:19.321 --> 00:12:22.951
- Orice sau pe cineva neobianuit ?
- Nimeni.

151
00:12:24.873 --> 00:12:27.482
Mulaumesc.
N-am alte antrebari.

152
00:12:33.566 --> 00:12:37.162
