176
00:13:57.327 --> 00:13:58.739
Vrei slujba sau nu ?

177
00:14:02.897 --> 00:14:04.097
Ramsey !

178
00:14:05.885 --> 00:14:07.882
- Cinci minute.
- Bine.

179
00:14:10.214 --> 00:14:12.224
E consilierul juridic Legrand ?

180
00:14:13.929 --> 00:14:17.971
Fuge de provocari ai ne-am ampotmolit
la juratul numarul trei.

181
00:14:18.609 --> 00:14:21.466
O moatenitoare a banilor obainuai
din petrol. care nu se gandeate

182
00:14:21.566 --> 00:14:24.012
decat la faptul ca oamenii
fura de la ea.

183
