nu e suficient de severa.

184
00:14:30.624 --> 00:14:33.088
Pe langa faptul ca eati fiica
lui Walter Brady.

185
00:14:33.188 --> 00:14:35.000
spune-mi altceva despre tine.

186
00:14:36.939 --> 00:14:39.652
Am absolvit an 2007 la Vanderbilt.

187
00:14:39.960 --> 00:14:41.436
Facultatea de drept din Columbia.

188
