191
00:14:53.176 --> 00:14:54.376
Sa ma liniatesc.

192
00:14:55.764 --> 00:14:57.164
La River Oaks ?

193
00:14:58.774 --> 00:15:00.074
Mulaumesc. tata.

194
00:15:00.442 --> 00:15:01.931
ai-au dat medicamente ?

195
00:15:04.122 --> 00:15:05.322
Nu-ai fie jena.

196
00:15:06.101 --> 00:15:08.261
