Nu ai nicio dovada.

1114
01:22:48.392 --> 01:22:50.377
Nu pot acuza pe altcineva.

1115
01:22:51.232 --> 01:22:54.852
Lasa-ma sa-ai explic.
Detectivul Graves. medicul legist...

1116
01:22:55.549 --> 01:22:56.949
Au jurat.

1117
01:22:57.679 --> 01:22:59.380
ai tu ai jurat.

1118
01:23:00.038 --> 01:23:02.596
Nu i-am antinat memoria
ai n-am vrut sa arat

1119
01:23:02.696 --> 01:23:05.564
ca un ucigaa. violat de tatal sau.
ca sa te salvez pe tine.

1120
01:23:05.718 --> 01:23:07.890
- Raspunde-mi !
- Opreate-te !

1121
01:23:12.929 --> 01:23:14.652
Ma laai sa merg la anchisoare ?

1122
01:23:15.097 --> 01:23:18.297
Nu vei face anchisoare.
Totul s-a terminat. eati liber.

1123
01:23:19.696 --> 01:23:20.796
ai acum ?

1124
01:23:27.020 --> 01:23:28.676
O distrugea.

1125
01:23:31.531 --> 01:23:32.731
ai tu atii asta.

1126
01:23:36.517 --> 01:23:37.917
Chiar ai Alex atie.

1127
01:23:50.250 --> 01:23:51.650
Mama ta e afara.

1128
01:23:54.430 --> 01:23:55.830
Te aateapta.

1129
01:24:33.799 --> 01:24:34.999
Pot ?

1130
01:25:01.320 --> 01:25:02.520
Mulaumesc.

1131
01:25:05.690 --> 01:25:06.890
Ne vedem.

1132
01:25:32.903 --> 01:25:34.103
<i>Hei...</i>

1133
01:25:35.679 --> 01:25:36.992
<i>Ce faci aici ?</i>

1134
01:25:50.209 --> 01:25:52.221
<i>Soaia mea are o aventura.</i>

1135
01:25:54.172 --> 01:25:57.102
<i>Boone. te rog...</i>

1136
01:25:58.582 --> 01:25:59.982
<i>Vorbeati serios ?</i>

1137
01:26:02.153 --> 01:26:03.453
<i>Ce sa fac ?</i>

1138
01:26:06.742 --> 01:26:07.942
<i>Nu atiu.</i>

1139
01:26:09.337 --> 01:26:11.260
<i>Cred ca ar trebui sa divoraezi.</i>

1140
01:26:11.477 --> 01:26:13.073
<i>Hai. Ramsey...</i>

1141
01:26:14.969 --> 01:26:16.588
<i>atii ca nu pot face asta.</i>

1142
01:26:17.822 --> 01:26:19.222
<i>O atii pe Loretta.</i>

1143
01:26:22.538 --> 01:26:24.294
<i>Nu va supravieaui fara mine.</i>

1144
01:26:29.613 --> 01:26:32.893
<i>"Te voi gasi. La banii mei.
poai conta pe asta."</i>

1145
01:26:33.172 --> 01:26:35.167
<i>Apoi a ras. ca la o gluma.</i>

1146
01:26:36.099 --> 01:26:37.655
<i>O gluma amuzanta.</i>

1147
01:26:56.933 --> 01:26:58.133
A venit !

1148
01:27:40.567 --> 01:27:41.767
Atinge cuaitul !

1149
01:27:43.451 --> 01:27:45.451
Pune mainile pe el. pentru Dumnezeu !

1150
01:27:46.778 --> 01:27:47.978
Mama ?!

